{"tid":1775774,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"【12.9】今日冇罷工嘅手足，入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-12-09T05:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T05:14:35.000Z","uid":79382,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6c87cb02e761596d6444931e1c0aae1e8606a901","tid":1775774,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:16:54.000Z","msg":"唔該即刻入以下呢個post！<br />\n<br />\n【緊急】十大工會要人！要人！要人！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1775649\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1775649</a><br />\n<br />\n而家冇工會支援，明白大家比較難話罷就罷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有手足整合咗各行各業成立工會嘅進度，<br />\n大家快啲搵返自己所屬工會，<br />\n時機一到，我哋要嚟次真嘅大三罷，<br />\n癱瘓香港經濟，迫使政府回應五大訴求 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2273d8781e025b34c46eb352a94c67df91a07be1","tid":1775774,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1124ec846c2a8d74689c5872c7e5ecaa3921da8f","tid":1775774,"uid":109211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"三罷狼來了feell"},{"pid":"7624e74dca6b2b70d8b037ac3a3ee66edbb70682","tid":1775774,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f2f444a557002f6f884765ba397b8e9dbad719","tid":1775774,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1124ec846c2a8d74689c5872c7e5ecaa3921da8f","tid":1775774,"uid":109211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:30:42.000Z","msg":"三罷狼來了feell"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T06:36:14.000Z","msg":"唔想再狼來了嘅話，<br />\n就要嚟次認真嘅！<br />\n我相信香港人，<br />\n行咗